com.i2group.apollo.model.schema

Enum AlertFeedPropertyTypeId

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<AlertFeedPropertyTypeId>
      • com.i2group.apollo.model.schema.AlertFeedPropertyTypeId
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.i2group.apollo.model.schema.ISystemPropertyTypeId, Serializable, Comparable<AlertFeedPropertyTypeId>

    public enum AlertFeedPropertyTypeId
extends Enum<AlertFeedPropertyTypeId>
implements com.i2group.apollo.model.schema.ISystemPropertyTypeId
    Provides a way to look up the property group type identifiers and property type identifiers for the system-defined item type named "Alert Feed".
